{"priority": "major", "kind": "bug", "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}ts=c_plus_plus"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "drcsim", "full_name": "osrf/drcsim", "uuid": "{247b5408-ae91-4e3c-b2f9-a21994658d11}"}, "links": {"attachments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/141/attachments_page=1.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/141.json"}, "watch": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/141/watch"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/141/comments_page=1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/drcsim/issues/141/atlasplugin-imu-bug-fix"}, "vote": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/drcsim/issues/141/vote"}}, "reporter": {"display_name": "Patrick Beeson", "uuid": "{d33f061a-d3c9-4b15-96cc-d08b463d97c6}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bd33f061a-d3c9-4b15-96cc-d08b463d97c6%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bd33f061a-d3c9-4b15-96cc-d08b463d97c6%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/initials/PB-0.png"}}, "nickname": "Patrick Beeson", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:eff3a3b0-e19b-43e6-b0a0-22d6a8721c3b"}, "title": "AtlasPlugin IMU Bug Fix", "component": null, "votes": 0, "watches": 1, "content": {"raw": "The AtlasPlugin IMU was giving bad readings when the robot was spawned with a non-zero pitch, roll, and or yaw.\r\n\r\nFound the bug.  Bad transform multiplication.\r\n\r\nPatch below:\r\n\r\n\r\n```\r\n#!c++\r\n\r\ndiff -r c69ecab26a55 ros/atlas_msgs/AtlasPlugin.cpp\r\n--- a/ros/atlas_msgs/AtlasPlugin.cpp\tWed Feb 27 11:19:18 2013 -0800\r\n+++ b/ros/atlas_msgs/AtlasPlugin.cpp\tThu Feb 28 18:49:14 2013 -0600\r\n@@ -624,7 +624,7 @@\r\n       {\r\n         // Get IMU rotation relative to Initial IMU Reference Pose\r\n         math::Quaternion imuRot =\r\n-          imuLinkPose.rot * this->imuReferencePose.rot.GetInverse();\r\n+          this->imuReferencePose.rot.GetInverse() * imuLinkPose.rot;\r\n \r\n         imuMsg.orientation.x = imuRot.x;\r\n         imuMsg.orientation.y = imuRot.y;\r\n\r\n```", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>The AtlasPlugin IMU was giving bad readings when the robot was spawned with a non-zero pitch, roll, and or yaw.</p>\n<p>Found the bug.  Bad transform multiplication.</p>\n<p>Patch below:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-c++\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"n\">diff</span> <span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">r</span> <span class=\"n\">c69ecab26a55</span> <span class=\"n\">ros</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">atlas_msgs</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">AtlasPlugin</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">cpp</span>\n<span class=\"o\">---</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">ros</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">atlas_msgs</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">AtlasPlugin</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">cpp</span>    <span class=\"n\">Wed</span> <span class=\"n\">Feb</span> <span class=\"mi\">27</span> <span class=\"mi\">11</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">19</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">18</span> <span class=\"mi\">2013</span> <span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">0800</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+++</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">ros</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">atlas_msgs</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">AtlasPlugin</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">cpp</span>    <span class=\"n\">Thu</span> <span class=\"n\">Feb</span> <span class=\"mi\">28</span> <span class=\"mi\">18</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">49</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">14</span> <span class=\"mi\">2013</span> <span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mo\">0600</span>\n<span class=\"err\">@@</span> <span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">624</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">7</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">624</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">7</span> <span class=\"err\">@@</span>\n       <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n         <span class=\"c1\">// Get IMU rotation relative to Initial IMU Reference Pose</span>\n         <span class=\"n\">math</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Quaternion</span> <span class=\"n\">imuRot</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span>\n<span class=\"o\">-</span>          <span class=\"n\">imuLinkPose</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rot</span> <span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"k\">this</span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">imuReferencePose</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rot</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">GetInverse</span><span class=\"p\">();</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span>          <span class=\"k\">this</span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">imuReferencePose</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rot</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">GetInverse</span><span class=\"p\">()</span> <span class=\"o\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">imuLinkPose</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rot</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n         <span class=\"n\">imuMsg</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">orientation</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">imuRot</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n         <span class=\"n\">imuMsg</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">orientation</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">y</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">imuRot</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "wontfix", "version": {"name": "2.1.0", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/drcsim/versions/49845.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-03-01T00:52:58.833316+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2013-03-04T21:47:14.986299+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 141}